---
import BaseHead from '../../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseHead title={`Privacy — Hermetrix`} description="Take back control of your digital life. Practical, no-nonsense privacy for individuals." />

<main class="privacy-root">
  <nav class="mini-nav" aria-label="privacy navigation">
    <ul>
      <li><a href="/" class="back">Back to Hermetrix</a></li>
      <li><a href="/individuals" aria-current="page">Privacy</a></li>
      <li><a href="/individuals/products">Products</a></li>
      <li><a href="/individuals/services">Services</a></li>
    </ul>
  </nav>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="wrap">
      <h1>Disappear from the surveillance grid</h1>
      <p class="lead">Tools and tactics for people who don't trust governments, corporations, or sloppy vendors.</p>
      <p class="sub">Practical digital self-defense — start today with steps that actually matter.</p>
      <div class="actions">
        <a class="cta" href="/individuals/products">Secure Your Digital Life</a>
        <a class="cta ghost" href="mailto:hello@hermetrix.nz?subject=Personal+Privacy+Help">Ask a Privacy Question</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="quick-steps">
    <div class="wrap">
      <h2>Start now — three immediate steps</h2>
      <ol>
        <li>Install a privacy-focused OS (GrapheneOS) on a spare phone or your main device.</li>
        <li>Move sensitive data to an encrypted 'data vault' and delete unnecessary cloud copies.</li>
        <li>Set up a trustworthy encrypted messaging and email stack, and use a good VPN only when necessary.</li>
      </ol>
      <p class="note">These are realistic, testable actions — no snake oil, only operational security.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="why">
    <div class="wrap">
      <h2>Why this is different</h2>
      <p>Most vendors sell you a product and call it "security". We teach operational security — the habits, choices, and trade-offs that actually reduce your exposure.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Radical transparency about risks and limitations</li>
        <li>No corporate buzzwords — just clear guidance</li>
        <li>Tools chosen for resilience, not marketing</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <Footer />
  </footer>
</main>

<style>
.privacy-root{--bg:#0b0f12;--panel:#0f1720;--muted:#9aa6b2;--accent:#66b3ff;--cta:#4fb0ff}
*{box-sizing:border-box}
.privacy-root{margin:0;background:var(--bg);color:#e6eef6;font-family:system-ui,-apple-system,Segoe UI,Roboto,Ubuntu,'Helvetica Neue',Arial;min-height:100vh;display:flex;flex-direction:column}
.mini-nav{padding:1rem;align-items:center;background:linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(255,255,255,0.01),transparent);}
.mini-nav ul{display:flex;gap:1rem;margin:0;padding:0;list-style:none}
.mini-nav a{color:var(--muted);text-decoration:none;font-weight:600}
.mini-nav .back{opacity:0.8}
.wrap{max-width:1000px;margin:0 auto;padding:2rem}
.hero{padding:3rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.03)}
.hero .lead{color:var(--accent);font-size:1.15rem;margin-top:.5rem}
.hero .sub{color:var(--muted);margin-top:.5rem}
.actions{margin-top:1.25rem;display:flex;gap:.75rem;flex-wrap:wrap}
.cta{background:var(--cta);color:#052036;padding:.75rem 1.25rem;border-radius:.5rem;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none}
.cta.ghost{background:transparent;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);color:var(--muted)}
.quick-steps{padding:2rem 0}
.quick-steps ol{margin:0;padding-left:1.1rem;color:var(--muted)}
.quick-steps li{margin:0.75rem 0}
.note{margin-top:1rem;color:var(--muted)}
.why{padding:2rem 0}
.why ul{list-style:disc;padding-left:1.2rem;color:var(--muted)}
@media(min-width:1200px){.wrap{max-width:1200px}.hero{padding:4rem 0}.wrap{padding:3rem}}
@media(max-width:640px){.wrap{padding:1rem}.hero h1{font-size:1.5rem}}
</style>
